---
import BaseLayout from "src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Articles from "@components/Articles.astro";

// Optimize our landing image and pass it as props to the BaseLayout (for preloading) and Landing (for rendering)
import { getOptimizedImage } from "@libs/utils";

// Import images
import landingImage from "@assets/images/grey-abstract-m.webp";
import landingDesktopImage from "@assets/images/grey-abstract.webp";
import seoPic from "@assets/images/svg/seo-pic.svg";

// Import SVG icons from @assets/images/svg directory
import seoIcon from "@assets/images/svg/seo.svg";
import piggyBankIcon from "@assets/images/svg/piggy-bank.svg";

// Optimize the landing image
const optimizedImage = await getOptimizedImage(landingImage);
---

<BaseLayout
  title="SEO"
  description="Learn how SEO benefits small businesses. Explore the differences between SEO and local SEO, and discover strategies to improve your online visibility and attract more customers."
  preloadedImage={optimizedImage}
>
  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!--                   Banner                     -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->

  <div id="banner-843">
    <div class="cs-container">
      <span class="cs-int-title">SEO</span>
    </div>
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <picture class="cs-background" aria-hidden="true">
      <!-- Mobile Image -->
      <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset={landingImage.src}>
      <!-- Tablet and above Image -->
      <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset={landingDesktopImage.src}>
      <img
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        src={landingDesktopImage.src}
        alt="grey abstract"
        width="1280"
        height="568"
      >
    </picture>
    <!-- SVG Wave -->
    <svg class="cs-wave" width="1920" height="179" viewBox="0 0 1920 179" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M1920 179V91.3463C1835.33 91.3463 1715.47 76.615 1549.2 32.9521C1299.48 -32.3214 1132.77 12.1006 947.32 61.5167C810.762 97.9044 664.042 137 466.533 137C331.607 137 256.468 123.447 188.082 111.113C130.974 100.812 78.5746 91.3609 0 91.3609V179H1920Z" fill="white" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!--                 Content Page                 -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->

  <section id="content-page-1401">
    <div class="cs-container">
      <div class="cs-image-group">
        <div class="cs-flex">
          <picture class="cs-background">
            <!-- Mobile Image -->
            <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset={seoPic.src}>
            <!-- Tablet and above Image -->
            <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset={seoPic.src}>
            <img
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              src={seoPic.src}
              alt="SEO illustration"
              width="542"
              height="728"
            >
          </picture>
        </div>
        <ul class="cs-card-group">
          <li class="cs-item">
            <h3 class="cs-h3">
              <img
                class="cs-h3-icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                src={seoIcon.src}
                alt="SEO icon"
                width="32"
                height="32"
              >
              Boost Your Visibility
            </h3>
            <p class="cs-item-text cs-text">
              SEO helps your business appear higher in search results, making it easier for potential customers to find you. Increase your online visibility and attract more targeted traffic to your website.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="cs-item">
            <h3 class="cs-h3">
              <img
                class="cs-h3-icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                src={piggyBankIcon.src}
                alt="Piggy bank icon"
                width="32"
                height="32"
              >
              Cost-Effective Marketing
            </h3>
            <p class="cs-item-text cs-text">
              Unlike paid advertising, SEO provides long-term benefits without ongoing costs. Invest in SEO to build a sustainable online presence and generate consistent organic traffic to your business.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
        <div class="cs-content">
            <h1 class="cs-title">Understanding SEO for Small Businesses</h1>

            <p class="cs-text">
                In today's digital age, having a strong online presence is crucial for the success of any business, especially small enterprises. Search Engine Optimization (SEO) plays a pivotal role in achieving this online visibility. By implementing effective SEO strategies, small businesses can significantly improve their chances of being discovered by potential customers, competing with larger companies, and growing their customer base.
            </p>

            <div class="cs-image-group d-lg-none d-block">
                <div class="cs-flex">
                    <picture class="cs-background">
                        <!-- Mobile Image -->
                        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset={seoPic.src}>
                        <!-- Tablet and above Image -->
                        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset={seoPic.src}>
                        <img
                          loading="lazy"
                          decoding="async"
                          src={seoPic.src}
                          alt="SEO illustration"
                          width="542"
                          height="728"
                        >
                      </picture>
                </div>
                <ul class="cs-card-group mt-3">
                    <li class="cs-item">
                        <h3 class="cs-h3">
                            <img
                            class="cs-h3-icon"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                            loading="lazy"
                            decoding="async"
                            src={seoIcon.src}
                            alt="SEO icon"
                            width="32"
                            height="32"
                          >
                          Boost Your Visibility
                        </h3>
                        <p class="cs-item-text cs-text">
                            SEO helps your business appear higher in search results, making it easier for potential customers to find you. Increase your online visibility and attract more targeted traffic to your website.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="cs-item">
                        <h3 class="cs-h3">
                            <img class="cs-h3-icon" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src={piggyBankIcon.src} alt="icon" width="32" height="32">
                            Cost-Effective Marketing
                        </h3>
                        <p class="cs-item-text cs-text">
                            Unlike paid advertising, SEO provides long-term benefits without ongoing costs. Invest in SEO to build a sustainable online presence and generate consistent organic traffic to your business.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3>What is SEO?</h3>
            <p class="cs-text">
                Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the practice of optimizing a website to increase its visibility and ranking in search engine results pages (SERPs). The goal is to attract more organic (non-paid) traffic to a website by improving its relevance and authority for specific search queries.
            </p>

            <h3>SEO vs Local SEO</h3>
            <p class="cs-text">
                While SEO and Local SEO share many similarities, they have distinct differences:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>SEO:</strong> Focuses on improving a website's visibility on a national or global scale. It's suitable for businesses that operate online or serve a wide geographic area.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Local SEO:</strong> Targets specific geographic locations and aims to improve visibility in local search results. It's ideal for businesses with physical locations or those serving particular localities.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>How SEO Benefits Small Businesses</h3>
            <p class="cs-text">
                SEO can provide numerous advantages for small businesses:
            </p>
            <ol>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Increased Visibility:</strong> Improves your chances of being found by potential customers searching for your products or services online.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Cost-Effective Marketing:</strong> Once established, SEO can provide a steady stream of organic traffic without ongoing advertising costs.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Credibility and Trust:</strong> Higher search rankings often translate to increased trust from potential customers.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Better User Experience:</strong> SEO practices often lead to improved website usability and faster load times.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Local Dominance:</strong> Local SEO helps small businesses compete with larger companies in their specific geographic area.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Long-Term Strategy:</strong> Unlike paid advertising, the effects of SEO can be long-lasting and compound over time.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Targeted Traffic:</strong> SEO helps attract users who are actively searching for your products or services, leading to higher conversion rates.</li>
            </ol>

            <h3>The Importance of Local Citations, Consistent NAP, and Google Business Profile Optimization</h3>
            <p class="cs-text">
                For small businesses focusing on local SEO, several factors play a crucial role:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Local Citations:</strong> These are online mentions of your business name, address, and phone number. Having your business listed in local directories, review sites, and industry-specific platforms can significantly boost your local SEO efforts.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Consistent NAP:</strong> NAP stands for Name, Address, and Phone number. Ensuring this information is consistent across all online platforms is vital for local SEO. Inconsistencies can confuse search engines and potential customers, potentially harming your search rankings.</li>
                <li class="cs-text"><strong>Google Business Profile:</strong> Formerly known as Google My Business, this free tool allows you to manage your business's online presence across Google, including Search and Maps. It's essential for local SEO as it helps your business appear in local search results, provides valuable information to potential customers, and allows you to engage with them through reviews and posts.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Conclusion</h3>
            <p class="cs-text">
                For small businesses, implementing a solid SEO strategy can level the playing field, allowing them to compete with larger companies and attract more customers. Whether focusing on general SEO or local SEO, the benefits can significantly impact a business's online presence and overall success.
            </p>

            <p class="cs-text">
                In conclusion, SEO is not just a luxury for big corporations; it's a necessity for businesses of all sizes. By understanding and implementing SEO strategies, including local SEO techniques like managing local citations, maintaining consistent NAP information, and optimizing your Google Business Profile, small businesses can dramatically improve their online visibility. This increased visibility translates to more website traffic, more foot traffic for physical stores, and ultimately, more customers and revenue. In the digital marketplace, a well-executed SEO strategy can be the difference between thriving and merely surviving.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-bubbles" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<Articles />

</BaseLayout>

